WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.640
Which window will be most acceptable for
哪个窗口最能接受

00:00:02.640 --> 00:00:06.675
an international business application to have scheduled downtime?
已安排停机时间的国际业务应用程序 ?

00:00:06.675 --> 00:00:11.190
The answer is, the first Saturday of the month from 1:00-4:00 AM.
答案是 从上午 1:00-4:00 开始的第一个星期六 

00:00:11.190 --> 00:00:13.380
The things we want to consider here are,
我们想考虑的是

00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:14.790
what is our user base,
我们的用户基地是什么

00:00:14.790 --> 00:00:17.460
and when are they likely to be using our application?
什么时候他们会使用我们的应用呢 ?

00:00:17.460 --> 00:00:20.490
Because we're talking about international customers,
因为我们说的是国际客户

00:00:20.490 --> 00:00:23.745
we should be very careful when assuming thing about time zones.
我们在假设时区的时候应该很谨慎

00:00:23.745 --> 00:00:26.985
However, since we're talking about a business application,
但是既然我们说的是商业应用

00:00:26.985 --> 00:00:31.300
we can't assume things about the workweek versus the weekend.
我们不能假设工作周和周末的事
